node.text: FULL VID AT LINK IN BIO! Karl is dabbling in the college athletics sponsorship game and his first stop: THE UNDERAPPRECIATED. The punters will compete for $5,000 and a #bassmobile visit and the winner will be chosen by whoever gets the most buzz about fishing! Follow all our punters and hashtag #karlpunts to see who wins this month! @paxton_brooks, @jbram15, @austin_mac_31, @gmckinniss, @andyvuj24, @raceporter, @evanfinegan40, @tgill1k, @porter_wilson

node.text: MAJOR NEWS: @catchcompany has acquired Recur Outdoors, the parent company of @postflyinc, @badfish, @waderods, and @pelicanreels. For years when people ask if we have a fly fishing box, I've been telling them "no" so to get a Postfly box, and not telling my bosses about that. I'm very excited to no longer have to recommend Postfly in the shadows as they are now a part of Catch Co.'s brands! We can't wait to welcome all of Recur's brands and employees aboard and bring all of them into this awesome community with all of you! IF YOU'VE READ THIS FAR, a nice little gift to get you started: use code CATCH at the link in our bio to get $15 off your first POSTFLY box!
